Revision history for the Potracheno time tracker project.

0.13    Mon Feb 26 2018
        BUG Catch up with neaf, fix login/register inconsistency

0.12    Mon Nov 6 2017
        ADM Added admin interface to ban/allow users
        ADM Added proper password reset links
        BIN Rework scripts
        BUG A lot of refactoring and bugfix

0.11    Sat Feb 11 2017
        UI  Add configurable front page & front page activity feed
        UI  Fix form alignment, redo screenshots
        UI  Add auto-update as in "new version available" in page footer
        BUG Fix time units: 1d=8h, 1w=5d
        REF Move to Neaf 0.14
        AUX Merge pull request #5 from Difrex/master - docker support
        BUG Fix <code></code> processing (was broken in Perl < 5.10)
        DOC Step-by-step installation instruction, Winows install OK
        BUG Lots of minor bugfixes

0.10    Thu Nov 3 2016
        DOC Help improved, modules renamed.

0.09    Fri Oct 28 2016
        DOC Add help index
        TPL Add manual password recovery help page
        APP Add stats page with overall & per-tag aggregate stats
        APP Add issue tags as space-separated hyphen-delimited alphanumeric characters
        UI  Add <qoute> and <plain> md tags, add #888 autolinks
        AUX Add initscript

0.08    Mon Oct 17 2016
        APP Add watched issues + in-app activity stream
        APP Add report showing ready to go solutions
        APP Add report & search pagination
        UI  Add <code> blocks to markdown
        DOC Make help actually describe UI and what to expect from it
        BUG A lot of bug fixes.

0.07    Tue Oct 11 2016
        APP Add markdown, preview, and edit to issues
        APP Add markdown to comments
        UI  Add fancy 404 & 403 stubs
        UI  Add some help
        UI  Move login_or_register to where it's due
        UI  Numerous UI fixes
        TST Add template correctness test

0.06    Sat Oct 08 2016
        CSS Redesign with bootstrap (by Poizon) 
        APP Comments added to search
        BUG Fix FindBin incompatibility under plackup
        AUX Rename bin/install.pl => Install.PL, better help & options

0.05    Sun Oct 02 2016
        REP Add issue report
        APP Add issue statuses
        APP Add solution proposals
        MOD Add mysql DB schema
        CSS Improve looks to some extent
        TST Add DB readiness test script (check-db.t)
        BUG Numerous bugs fixed, even more added

0.04    Sun Sep 25 2016
        TPL Don't show forms to anon user
        MOD Add migrate.pl for dump, restore
        MOD Add config (local/potracheno.cfg); add lostpass.pl for resetting password
        CSS Add css, logo & table layout. Still needs work tho
        REF Rename app.psgi => bin/potracheno.psgi
        APP Add some crude change password
        UXP Use pretty time

0.03    Sat Sep 24 2016
        APP Add login, register support
        APP Add search for issues
        APP Add user detail page, very primitive for now
        APP Add comments & wasted time
        APP Add local sqlite, add time_spent
        MOD sqlite-based model with tests

0.01    Mon Sep 19 2016
        Crude in-memory version started out
